<p>使用递归进行操作时，关键是设置好递归条件。斐波那契数列的定义如下：</p><p><a href="http://c.hiphotos.baidu.com/zhidao/pic/item/fcfaaf51f3deb48f9695e772f51f3a292cf57899.jpg" target="_blank" title="点击查看大图" class="ikqb_img_alink"><img class="ikqb_img" src="http://c.hiphotos.baidu.com/zhidao/wh%3D600%2C800/sign=9d55d75e781ed21b799c26e39d5ef1fc/fcfaaf51f3deb48f9695e772f51f3a292cf57899.jpg" esrc="http://c.hiphotos.baidu.com/zhidao/wh%3D450%2C600/sign=0114def2d8c451daf6a304ef83cd7e50/fcfaaf51f3deb48f9695e772f51f3a292cf57899.jpg" /></a></p><p>&nbsp;f2 = f0 + f1 = 0 + 1 = 1，所以条件可以设置成当n==1或者n==2时，返回1。其它项则依次递归调用即可。</p><pre t="code" l="cpp">#include&nbsp;&lt;stdio.h&gt;<br />int&nbsp;f(int&nbsp;n){<br />if(n==1&nbsp;||&nbsp;n==2)<br />return&nbsp;1;<br />else<br />return&nbsp;(f(n-2)+f(n-1));<br />}<br />int&nbsp;main(){<br />const&nbsp;int&nbsp;num&nbsp;=&nbsp;20;<br />int&nbsp;i;<br />for(i=1;i&lt;=num;i++){<br />printf(&quot;%-6d&quot;,f(i));<br />if(i%5==0)<br />printf(&quot;\n&quot;);<br />}<br />printf(&quot;\n&quot;);<br />return&nbsp;0;<br />}</pre><p><a href="http://a.hiphotos.baidu.com/zhidao/pic/item/42a98226cffc1e170234cd9d4f90f603728de997.jpg" target="_blank" title="点击查看大图" class="ikqb_img_alink"><img class="ikqb_img" src="http://a.hiphotos.baidu.com/zhidao/wh%3D600%2C800/sign=fab8786fd2ca7bcb7d2ecf298e39475b/42a98226cffc1e170234cd9d4f90f603728de997.jpg" esrc="http://a.hiphotos.baidu.com/zhidao/wh%3D450%2C600/sign=7aa9ca956e63f6241c083107b274c7ce/42a98226cffc1e170234cd9d4f90f603728de997.jpg" /></a></p>
